# MATLAB Mex build outputs.
# .mexmaca64 (Apple Silicon) and .mexmaci64 (Intel Mac) for the four
# committed .cpp filters live under filters/ and were checked in pre-v0.1.7.
# From v0.1.7 onward, freshly-built .mex* binaries should not be committed —
# MATLAB users regenerate them by running CMF_install.m. Existing committed
# binaries stay until a future release decides to remove them.
*.mex*
!filters/CMF_medfiltCirc2DMex.mexmaca64
!filters/CMF_medfiltCirc2DMex.mexmaci64
!filters/CMF_medfiltCirc2DQuantMex.mexmaca64
!filters/CMF_medfiltCirc2DQuantMex.mexmaci64
!filters/CMF_medfiltGeoRN2DMex.mexmaci64
